Description: Loctite Fire Block Foam is a specially designed insulating foam to fill gaps and resist the migration of fire and hot gasses in Type V residential (wood frame) construction. This foam is orange in color and is easily identifiable on the jobsite. Best for use where any fire rated foam is needed such as electrical, plumbing and HVAC penetrations. UL Certified and ASTM tested.
Item Name: Loctite Fireblock 12 oz. Spray Foam Sealant

Description: Loctite Polyseamseal All-Purpose Caulk is a premium grade water-based caulk designed to have the strength of an adhesive and the sealing characteristics of a caulk. Since it is latex based, this adhesive caulk is easy to apply and tool. It has very low odor, so it is perfect for indoor projects. Loctite Polyseamseal All-Purpose Sealant is environmentally safe and easy to clean up with just soap and water. Once fully cured after 24 hours, this unique caulking is weather-resistant, mold and mildew resistant, as well as paintable after 40 minutes. This sealant was designed to be a multiple use adhesive and caulk and can be used for almost any household or remodeling project. It is excellent for gluing loose molding or tiles, securing backsplashes, setting sinks and even repairing or concealing small cracks in plaster, drywall or around molding and baseboards. Loctite Polyseamseal All-Purpose Sealant can even help to lower energy costs by sealing air leaks around windows and doors as well as other utility and plumbing penetrations. The permanently flexible seal provides a long lasting, professional finish for any household project.
Item Name: Loctite Polyseamseal All Purpose 10 oz. Clear Latex Caulk Sealant

Description: Loctite Pro Gaps and Cracks Foam is a fire rated insulating foam sealant that fills gaps up to 1 in. to seal out air, moisture and pests. This foam is ready to be used with any standard foam gun applicator which provides superior control and reusability. This foam is recommended for standard gap filling applications like wiring, plumbing and HVAC penetrations. It can also be used in areas where a fire rated foam is needed. The foam is orange in color and is designed to resist the migration of fire and hot gasses in Type V residential (wood frame) construction.
Item Name: Loctite Pro Gaps and Cracks 21 oz. Spray Foam Sealant

Description: Loctite Clear Silicone is a multipurpose adhesive and sealant which creates a permanent waterproof, protective seal that is ideal for metal, glass, rubber, tile and porcelain. Designed for indoor and outdoor use, Loctite Clear Silicone Waterproof Sealant can repair everything from electrical connections to seams on boots to stop leaks in wet weather as well as saltwater or freshwater aquariums. This all-season sealant creates durable, flexible bonds that resist extreme temperatures and impact and won't crack, peel, or shrink. Excellent for use on imperfect surfaces and filling gaps and bonds ABS, glass, ceramic, porcelain, wood, aluminum, stainless steel, cultured marble, fiberglass, granite, vinyl tile, some rubbers and plastics. Loctite Clear Silicone Waterproof Sealant is Aquarium Safe and can be used for sealing or repairing sinks, tubs, aquariums, plumbing fixtures, door frames, windows, vents, toys, appliances, gaskets, weather-stripping, outside of fireplace doors, and shoes and boots as well. Not recommended for use on the following plastics: polyethylene, polypropylene, polytetrafluoroethylene (PTFE), polymethylmethacrylate (PMMA), polycarbonate or PVC. Not recommended for use on marble, limestone, cement, concrete, brass, copper, magnesium, iron, zinc or galvanized metals.
Item Name: Loctite Silicone Waterproof Multipurpose Adhesive Sealant 2.7 oz. Clear Tube

Description: Loctite TITE FOAM Big Gaps is a new generation of polyurethane-based insulating foam sealant that expands to fill, seal, and effectively insulate gaps and cracks up to 3 in. in size, inside and out! Loctite TITE FOAM Big Gaps is a bright white color and offers premium durability with its high density, flexibility, strong adhesion and UV resistance. Use to seal out air, moisture and pests in basements or crawlspaces, attic hatches and plumbing, HVAC or electrical penetrations. Quick and convenient to use and apply TITE FOAM Big Gaps offers an easy insulating spray foam option. It is recommended for use in both interior and exterior environments and is sandable and paintable.
Item Name: Loctite TITE FOAM Big Gaps Spray Foam, Bright White, 12 oz. Can, Insulating Spray Foam Sealant

Description: The warm, rich color and timeless beauty of Mendocino Redwood creates a breathtaking first impression. Beyond first impressions, it blends into the landscape creating a peaceful and relaxing natural outdoor living environment. With simple care and maintenance, your redwood deck, fence and outdoor living structures will provide decades of excellent performance, and long-lasting value. Mendocino Redwood is one of nature's finest and strongest building materials with shear strength up to five times greater than other decking materials. Whether you're building a deck, fence, play set or outdoor living structure; the enduring strength of redwood means safety and security for those that matter most. Nature can be harsh on outdoor living spaces - but Mendocino Redwood naturally stands up to the elements, insects, decay, warping, and splitting. All while staying comfortable on bare feet even on the hottest, sunniest days. Using energy-efficient natural redwood products helps store carbon instead of energy-intensive manufactured products that release carbon, therefore lowering your carbon footprint and reducing carbon emissions. Whether you are a frequent entertainer, or prefer to relax in the quiet of your own home, decks, fences, landscapes, and garden structures made of real redwood make for a beautiful addition. Mendocino Redwood is a high-quality, long-lasting, eco-friendly building material, which makes it the right choice for outdoor construction projects.
Item Name: Mendocino Forest Products 1-3/8 in. x 1-3/8 in. x 12 ft. B Heart S4S Redwood Lumber
